<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 02 May 2026 12:42:22 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>Coinbase 表示已就加密市场法案的关键部分达成协议</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-01/coinbase-says-deal-reached-on-key-part-of-crypto-market-bill</link><description>Coinbase Global Inc. 表示，已经就关键的稳定币收益率条款达成协议，这可能为美国参议院推进全面的加密立法扫清道路。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iRqfhCQom89o/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Fri, 01 May 2026 22:11:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-05-01/coinbase-says-deal-reached-on-key-part-of-crypto-market-bill</guid></item><item><title>比特币内部 2026：忠实者超越价格的一年</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-30/inside-bitcoin-2026-the-year-the-faithful-outgrew-the-price</link><description>比特币品牌的销售已经超越了图表。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iEYAiZlK4sDw/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-04-30/inside-bitcoin-2026-the-year-the-faithful-outgrew-the-price</guid></item><item><title>拉斯维加斯比特币的大力支持者努力策划反弹</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/bitcoin-faithful-came-to-las-vegas-but-the-price-didn-t-show-up</link><description>每年有那么几天，世界上最狂热的比特币信徒会戴着橙色牛仔帽、系着领带、穿着 T 恤聚集在一起，高呼价值 100 万美元的比特币。今年，在拉斯维加斯，这些口号对每个人都有效——除了市场。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iYXzZtn8oNlc/v2/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Apr 2026 17:56:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-04-30/bitcoin-faithful-came-to-las-vegas-but-the-price-didn-t-show-up</guid></item></channel></rss>